.DT
add_quest
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
add_quest

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_quest -  This method adds a new quest into the system.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int add_quest(string name,
int level,
int xp,
string title,
string story)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name of the quest
%^BOLD%^level%^RESET%^ - the level of the quest 0-100
%^BOLD%^title%^RESET%^ - the title for finishing the quest, 0 for none
%^BOLD%^story%^RESET%^ - the story about the quest
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if successful, 0 if not
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/quest_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds a new quest into the system.  You only need to call
this ONCE.  The name of the quest must be unique.  The story is
what can be seen in the players books about the player.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
delete_quest(), query_quest_level(), query_quest_title(), query_quest_story()

.EP

